---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Rumi
  Translator: Coleman Barks
  Author: Rumi
  ISBN: 978-0060845971
  Publisher: HarperOne
Format: Verse
By: Rumi
Title: Imagining Is Like
Description: February 20
---
Imagining is like feeling around
in a dark lane, or washing
your eyes with blood.

You are the truth
from foot to brow. Now,
what else would you like to know?
